Package: tLOH
Version: 0.99.0
Type: Package
Date: 2021-04-22
Title: Assessment of evidence for LOH in spatial transcriptomics pre-processed 
    data using Bayes factor calculations
Author: Michelle Webb, David Craig
Maintainer: Michelle Webb <michelgw@usc.edu>
Description: This tool requires spatial transcriptomics gene expression cluster
    data and allele count information at likely heterozygous single-nucleotide 
    polymorphism (SNP) positions. A Bayes factor is calculated to determine 
    evidence for either the heterozygous event or potential loss of 
    heterozygosity event.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/USCDTG/tLOH
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: knitr
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: scales,
    stats,
    utils,
    ggplot2, 
    data.table,
    purrr,
    dplyr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: CopyNumberVariation, Transcription, SNP, GeneExpression, 
    Transcriptomics
